{"id": "1432994035508711424", "channel_id": "1432994035508711424", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "有许多作品很优秀，却因种种现实原因离开了舞台。\n\n这是这类作品的宿命。\n\n我们在去年也曾经面临解散的危机。\n\n也因此懂得“不被遗忘”的珍贵。\n\n就如同我们的故事一样。\n\n在忘却前夜里，我们想给他们一个能被再次遇见的地方。\n\nMany creations are excellent, yet leave the stage for various real-world reasons.\n\nSuch is the fate of works of this kind.\n\nWe, too, faced the crisis of disbandment last year.\nAnd so we understand the preciousness of not being forgotten.\n\nJust like in our own story.\n\nIn Morimens, we hope to give them a place where they can be encountered once more.", "timestamp": "2025-10-29T07:26:41.807000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "goodjob1", "emoji_id": "1356083729558274149", "count": 50}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 24}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1356053116260454534", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1400771650064089112", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "🦐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Sendflowers", "emoji_id": "1400771545370067118", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "🥺", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "1068871527002558484", "emoji_id": "1072438754888908851", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432994035508711424", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "致敬那些不该被遗忘的创作 Tribute to works that should not be forgotten", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
